data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
This wizard will guide you through the process of mapping your buttons and axes to the Pad Tie standard virtual gamepad layout. After this, your gamepad will be remembered and all configurations will feel natural :-)
Click Start below to begin.

data.name: label3.Text
data.value: Press the button which closest matches the one indicated above. If your gamepad supports DPad/analog swapping, make sure it is disabled. If the DPad and left analog are in the opposite positions on your pad, you should press the D-pad when prompted for the D-pad, etc

data.name: finishedLbl.Text
data.value:
Your gamepad buttons have been mapped!
Would you like to upload your mapping for '%' so we can provide out-of-the-box support for this gamepad in the next release? We will only send the button mappings and the product ID information for your game controller.
